text: Pinkett may refer to: *Allen Pinkett (born 1964), former professional American football player *Eric Pinkett (1911–1979), the founder of the Leicestershire Schools Symphony Orchestra *Harold T. Pinkett (1914-2001), the first African- American archivist employed at the National Archives of the United States *Jada Pinkett Smith (born 1971), American actress, producer, director, author, singer-songwriter and businesswoman *Mary Pinkett, the first black New York City councilwoman *Randal Pinkett (born 1971), business consultant who was 2005 winner of The Apprentice *Ward Pinkett (1906–1937), American jazz trumpeter
